controller

Class CrackController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.CrackController

  • public class CrackController
extends java.lang.Object
    Crack class is a Nested Class under the BrickController abstract class as it is a feature of the Brick class. Responsible for all the implementations regarding the crack generated when a ball makes an impact with a brick.
